Interface CleaningStyle

All Known Implementing Classes:
DryClean, LaundryItem, WetClean
public interface CleaningStyle
Defines the cleaning style rates for laundry items. These rates are used to calculate the total cost of laundry items based on the cleaning type.
Version:
23.0
